			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1) With the debugbook, go to Act 3 -> Undercity -> Bhaal Temple -> Bhaal Temple Bridge.\r\n2) oe BTSetKilledGortash for Gortash killed\r\n3) oe BTUnholyAssassin for Unholy Assassin title.\r\n4) oe BTSetKilledSarevok for Sarevok killed.\r\n5) oe BTSetWarnedOrin for Orin was warned. If you set this, as you approach Orin, she will kill the victim first before you can talk to her. (Another dialog file)\r\n6) Go into the Bhaal Temple and trigger conversation with Orin."
				},
